App-Notifier-Service
====================

This distribution provides a Dancer-based web service for handling
notifications (e.g: for completion of events). See
https://metacpan.org/release/App-Notifier-Client for a sample command line
client to invoke notifications.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

after you install all of its dependencies.

Alternatively use the CPAN.pm module:

    # perl -MCPAN -e 'install App::Notifier::Service'

Or the CPANPLUS.pm module

    # perl -MCPANPLUS -e 'install App::Notifier::Service'

